txt.en: One should be careful when traversing the domain of Borangos, for many creatures of fire lurk within the caverns of Nargroth. You decide to defeat some of these creatures as you delve further into fire.
Nargroth is located in Talath Úrui.\n\nYou should defeat fire grims, Ghâsh-hai, and flame-spirits in Nargroth.
Defeated many fire grims, Ghâsh-hai, and flame-spirits in Nargroth.
Nargroth is located in Talath Úrui.\n\nYou should defeat fire grims, Ghâsh-hai, and flame-spirits in Nargroth.
Nargroth, the caverns of fire, is home to many creatures of flame.
You have successfully defeated many fire grims, Ghâsh-hai, and flame-spirits in Nargroth. While Borangos's army is vast, it is not infinite.
Defeat fire grims, Ghâsh-hai, and flame-spirits in Nargroth
